title: I Am What God Says I Am | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: I Am What God Says I Am | Joel Osteen
description:
God is the great architect of the universe. He put in you exactly what you need to live a victorious life. Get in agreement with God and say what He says about you.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
